snippet.title: MythForce - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
MythForce is coming to Nintendo Switch in 2023! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/mythforce-switch/

Step into a Saturday morning cartoon and adventure through crypts and castles with your friends in MythForce, a first-person melee roguelike game.

#MythForce #NintendoSwitch #NintendoDirect

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! http://www.nintendo.com/
